    "title": "Senior Plant Manager at Greaves Cotton",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Plant Manager looking for your next big career move? Greaves Cotton in Surat offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Greaves Cotton:\nGreaves Cotton is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Flexible working hours\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Greaves Cotton!",
